bulkDecompression.modal.title: Compressed files handling
bulkDecompression.confirm.closeWhileRunn: A task is running. Close and cancel it?
bulkDecompression.tip.extractToNewDirect: Extract to new directory(we will use file name without extension as the new directory name)
bulkDecompression.tip.deleteSourceAfterD: Delete the source file after decompression
bulkDecompression.tip.moveToParentDirect: Move all files and folders located in the extraction target directory to the parent directory of the compressed file. Note that any files or folders not contained in the compressed file, but present in the directory where the compressed file is being extracted, will also be moved to the parent directory.
bulkDecompression.warning.dangerousOpera: You have set 'Move to parent directory' without 'Extract to new directory' for {{count}} item(s). This is a dangerous combination that may cause unexpected behavior:
bulkDecompression.warning.allEntriesWill: All file system entries in the same directory will be moved to parent folder
bulkDecompression.warning.pendingFilesMa: Pending compressed files may be moved before decompression, causing failures
bulkDecompression.warning.fileStructureM: The final file structure may be completely messed up
bulkDecompression.tip.recommendation: However, for some cases we recommend users to make this choice. Please make sure you clearly understand what will happen.
